15,01What Exactly Is Marriage??
15,01-  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -  -
15,01 
15,01"Marriage is when you get to keep your girl and don't have to give
15,01her back to her parents"
15,01         -Eric, AGE 6
15,01 
15,01"When somebody's been dating for a while, the boy might propose to
15,01the girl. He says to her, 'I'll take you for a whole life, or at
15,01least until we have kids and get divorced, but you got to do one
15,01particular thing for me.'  Then she says yes, but she's wondering
15,01what the thing is and whether it's naughty or not. She can't wait to
15,01find out."
15,01         -Anita, AGE 9
